Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.12,0:01:41.62,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}歌声の止む時は　運命の終わり
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:49.51,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}そうとだけ決めていた　故は分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.76,0:01:57.47,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}金色も褪せるほど　焦がれてるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:02:04.65,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}憧れの輪郭は　遠ざかってくみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:11.99,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}溢れるよ　ほら手のひら　握り返してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.49,0:02:16.45,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(190,200)}痛みと痛みとりがえよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.45,0:02:20.20,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,0)}糧にするんだ　落花の欠片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:23.92,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(0,200)}全て傷ついて僕は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:28.29,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,50)}かたどってく　かたちになる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:33.84,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(50,200)}目覚めの先で　往こう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:38.26,OP JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}ずっと　響かせよう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.12,0:01:41.62,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}歌聲止息之時  就是命運的終點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:49.51,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}我只知這樣的結論  卻不知其原因
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.76,0:01:57.47,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的渴望之情能使黃金褪色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:02:04.65,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而憧憬的輪廓  卻似乎漸行漸遠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:11.99,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我思緒漫溢  快來握緊我的手心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.49,0:02:16.45,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(190,200)}用苦痛來交換苦痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.45,0:02:20.20,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,0)}用落花殘片充當食糧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:23.92,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(0,200)}我用所有創傷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:28.29,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,50)}模仿著塑造自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:33.84,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(50,200)}向著覺醒的前方前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:38.26,OP CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}讓歌聲永遠傳唱
Comment: 0,0:24:13.93,0:24:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ending-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:06.35,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I still remember you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.35,0:22:08.81,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The time we shared
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:11.39,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The love you gave
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:16.36,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Though everything has changed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.36,0:22:21.07,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You push me to live on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.07,0:22:30.91,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}海よりも深い奥底から見守っている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.91,0:22:36.50,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分かれた未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.13,0:22:44.13,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I still love you, even though I miss you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:53.06,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}永久に続く悲しみの夜の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.06,0:22:57.90,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愛は生きる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.82,0:23:03.57,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I will be here for you, always and forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.57,0:23:09.83,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今もずっと願っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.83,0:23:20.80,ED JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}温かいこの闇の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:06.35,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我依然記得你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.35,0:22:08.81,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}記得我們共度的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:11.39,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}記得你給予我的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:16.36,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}儘管一切都已面目全非
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.36,0:22:21.07,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你仍是我活著的動力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.07,0:22:30.91,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自比海更深的幽穴深底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.91,0:22:36.50,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}守護著各自分歧的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.13,0:22:44.13,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我依然愛著你  即使我只能思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:53.06,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在通向永恆的哀慟深夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.06,0:22:57.90,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}猶自有愛存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.82,0:23:03.57,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會為你守在這裡  始終如一  直到永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.57,0:23:09.83,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我仍將繼續為你祈願
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.83,0:23:20.80,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在這溫暖的黑暗之中
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Sign-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:17.89,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:20.93,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}小孩子很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:35.00,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雕刻她使我極其過癮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:36.21,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有幸整飾這枚樂器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.25,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}帶給我絕頂的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.09,0:06:41.17,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}去吧  人類孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:44.01,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只要你與石頭同在  價值就會延續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:28.42,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大家一起上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:28.46,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}當然了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.70,0:12:45.20,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}對！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:05.18,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拜託了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.32,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}鐵絲隊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:20.61,Caption_Cinema_10,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}壓住它！
